&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re now looking for a Head of Product to join the Economist AI Lab. This is a full-time position at the centre of our AI research and innovation programme. This is a unique opportunity to work with a small team that is shaping how one of the world&#39;s most respected media brands adapts to advances in AI.&lt;/p&gt;
