&lt;p&gt;This role will suit someone who thrives in uncertain, formative environments; who can connect new technical capabilities to customer needs; and who relishes the challenge of shaping the future rather than merely refining current practices.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This role will be based in our London headquarters.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
