&lt;li&gt;Coordinate design, research and technical exploration efforts to turn ideas into testable product and service concepts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Turn a vision into reality - creating the appropriate product briefs and user stories&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead early-stage testing and validation efforts - from problem framing, to research, to user testing and beta launches - and help us determine what’s worth scaling&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with editorial, technology, business and external stakeholders to ensure Lab initiatives are well-connected to broader strategic goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
